description: The Simpson's Quote Finder will take any quote you can kind-of/sort-of remember from the show The Simpson's and find the episode it belongs to. This Skill makes use of SimpsonQuotes.com's search API but is in no way affiliated with FX Networks LLC who owns the rights to The Simpson's.
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask Simpson's Quote Finder About Purple Monkey Dishwasher
Alexa Ask Simpson's Quote Finder for Help
name: Unofficial Simpson's Quote Finder
shortDescription: Give us a Simpson's Quote and we'll find the episode it belongs to
